Technical skills:
At least 5 years of relevant work experience in data engineering and data operations;
Hands-on experience with handling different file types (CSV, XLSX, JSON, TXT) in Python;
Proficient in using the Django framework for data modeling and SQL transformations (DDL generation of data sources, script generation and logging);
Good knowledge of the AWS data stack and services (such as S3, Lambda and RDS);
